OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWeak competition added 6p  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto supermarket fuel prices 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Drivers paid an extra 6p per litre for 
OL,6, fuel last year at supermarkets because 
OL,7, of weaker competition, a watchdog says.
OL,9,FThe Competition and Markets Authority  
OL,10,F(CMA) said supermarkets are usually the
OL,11,Fcheapest places to buy fuel but that   
OL,12,Fbig retailers had put up their margins.
OL,14,FThe regulator recommended a "fuel      
OL,15,Ffinder scheme" to help drivers find    
OL,16,Fbetter prices online.                  
OL,18,FBoss Sarah Cardell said competition was
OL,19,F"not working as well as it should be   
OL,20,Fand something needs to change swiftly".
